Uniquely Accomplished
        


            


	







                            
                            One-to-One Technology
KINDERGARTEN THROUGH 12
 

All Upper Arlington students, from elementary to high school, have one-to-one access to a technological device that appropriately supports and maximizes their learning. This program supplements existing strategies to personalize learning for all students. Learn More
 
                            
                            
                        
                    

                


	







                            
                            Advanced Programs of Study


COLLEGE CREDIT OPPORTUNITIES


 

Through Advanced Placement courses, the International Baccalaureate program and the College Credit Plus program, Upper Arlington students can choose from a variety of opportunities to experience college-level coursework and get a head start on earning college credit. Learn more
 
                            
                            
                        
                    

                


	







                            
                            Golden Bear Tradition
144 STATE CHAMPIONSHIPS

 

 Upper Arlington High School is proud to be home to 144 state championships since the 1930s. Our student athletes participate in 32 varsity sports at the high school, and each year several go on to pursue athletics at the college level. Learn more
 
                            
                            
                        
                    

                


	







                            
                            Legacy of Excellence
ACHIEVEMENTS IN THE ARTS

 

From ceramics classes to musical productions to symphony strings, our students have numerous and varied opportunities to explore every facet of the visual and performing arts. Our student artists and musicians are frequently recognized on the state and national level. Learn more
 
                            
                            
                        
                    

                


	







                            
                            Commitment to Community
SERVICE LEARNING FOCUS

 

Upper Arlington Schools has a long history of providing engaging and relevant learning experiences that meet real community needs. Students of all grade levels engage in meaningful service-learning opportunities, which help to instill a lifelong commitment to community. Learn more  
                            
                            
                        
                    

                
        


    


